# CodeDNA v0.3

This project uses CodeDNA. Every source file begins with a manifest header.

On EDIT:
- Update LAST_MODIFIED first
- Read DEPENDS_ON before changing signatures
- Follow @REQUIRES-READ before writing logic
- Apply @MODIFIES-ALSO changes in same session

On CREATE:
- Write manifest header before imports
- Set CONTEXT_BUDGET: always (core) | normal (standard) | minimal (utility)
- Add @REQUIRES-READ/@MODIFIES-ALSO to cross-file functions

EXPORTS are contracts — never rename without instruction.

Manifest format:
# === CODEDNA:0.3 ===
# FILE: name.ext
# PURPOSE: ≤15 words
# CONTEXT_BUDGET: always|normal|minimal
# DEPENDS_ON: file → symbol | none
# EXPORTS: fn(args) → type
# LAST_MODIFIED: ≤8 words
# ==================
